   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[11 lines of magical words and symbols] Drive Ptolemais whom Helene bore to Ptolemaios whom [l. 15] Didyme bore.  Inflame the liver and the spirit and the heart and the soul of this woman until she rushes forth and comes, Ptolemais, whom [l. 20] Helene bore to Ptolemaios whom Didyme bore, now, fast.</ab>
